OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1775736665
OL,3,CMan jailed for causing explosion at
OL,4,Chis home after family dispute
OL,6,FA man has been jailed for 11 years for
OL,7,Fcausing a house explosion by
OL,8,Fdeliberately cutting a gas pipe.
OL,10,FThe explosion at a terraced house in
OL,11,FEden Street, Derby, also severely
OL,12,Fdamaged two neighbouring properties on
OL,13,Fthe evening of 10 June last year. All
OL,14,Fthree properties had to be demolished.
OL,16,FPaul Solway, 58, disconnected the gas
OL,17,Fmain in the basement of his house and
OL,18,Fthen set fire to a chair in the
OL,19,Fkitchen, which caused the gas to
OL,20,Fignite. It was after a dispute with
OL,21,Fhis partner, who he was living with.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/5
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
