OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1775736665
OL,3,CMan jailed for causing explosion at
OL,4,Chis home after family dispute
OL,6,FHe was the only person in the house at
OL,7,Fthe time, and he and his family dog
OL,8,Fhad to be rescued from the rubble.
OL,10,FWhen Solway was arrested, he told
OL,11,Fpolice he had no recollection of the
OL,12,Fday and that he would not have
OL,13,Ftampered with the gas main.
OL,15,FDoorbell footage captured the house
OL,16,Fexplosion on Eden Street
OL,18,FSolway was seriously injured and spent
OL,19,Fseveral weeks in hospital with severe
OL,20,Fburns. His dog went on to make a full
OL,21,Frecovery.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/5
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1775736665
OL,3,CMan jailed for causing explosion at
OL,4,Chis home after family dispute
OL,6,FSolway, of no fixed address, admitted
OL,7,Fdamaging property being reckless as to
OL,8,Fwhether life was endangered.
OL,10,FHe has been sentenced to 11 years and
OL,11,Fmust serve two-thirds of that sentence
OL,12,Fbefore being considered for release.
OL,14,FResidents in Eden Street were forced
OL,15,Fto leave their homes for several days
OL,16,Fwhile demolition work took place.
OL,18,FSeveral other properties and vehicles
OL,19,Fparked nearby were also damaged.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/5
