PN,37404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1775736665
OL,3,CMan jailed for causing explosion at
OL,4,Chis home after family dispute
OL,6,FDerbyshire Police Detective Constable
OL,7,FShaun Carter, who led the
OL,8,Finvestigation, said: "Solway's
OL,9,Fdecision to cut this gas pipe left him
OL,10,Fin hospital but also caused distress
OL,11,Fand devastation to other members of
OL,12,Fthe community in Derby.
OL,14,F"Almost a year has passed since this
OL,15,Fincident yet many families are still
OL,16,Fdealing with the impact of his
OL,17,Freckless and dangerous actions.
OL,26,@pD@VOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/5
